  <h4>Rules for Eco rewards</h4>
  <p>1.Every day at 0:00 (UTC+8), the system collects the Eco point earned the day before, converts them proportionally to DCC tokens, and deliver DCCs into the user’s wallet. Then, Eco points will start from 0.</p>
  <p>2. Verification rewards are only available for first-time verification in each category (ID, bank account and carrier)</p>
  <p>3.There’s no daily limit to loan application rewards.</p>
